Package gobblin.source.extractor.extract.kafka

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    KafkaDeserializerExtractor
    Extension of KafkaExtractor that wraps Kafka's Deserializer API.
    KafkaDeserializerSource
    Extension of KafkaSource that returns a KafkaDeserializerExtractor.
    KafkaGsonDeserializer
    Implementation of Deserializer that deserializes Kafka data into a JsonElement using the StandardCharsets.UTF_8 encoding.
    KafkaWrapper Deprecated
    - Use GobblinKafkaConsumerClient
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    KafkaDeserializerExtractor.Deserializers
    Pre-defined Deserializer that can be referenced by the enum name.
